imap_body(): Argument #3 ($flags) must be a bitmask of FT_UID, FT_PEEK, and FT_INTERNAL

Warning: imap_body(): Bad message number in %s on line %d
bool(false)

Warning: imap_body(): UID does not exist in %s on line %d
